All source files should be in src dir.

Main script - grdl.sh

Script commands:
    grdl.sh COMMAND

grdl.sh command options:
    clean - remove all temp files and folders
    build - compile sources from src/ into build/
    jar [MainClassName] - make executable jar. If class name is not provided,
                          searches for file with ///MainClass// comment and
                          uses it as main class.
        example: ./grdl.sh jar App
    jjar [MainClassName] - make jar exec and clean. If class name is not provided,
                           searches for file with ///MainClass// comment and
                           uses it as main class.

Note:
    Script requires javac command available from shell